## Agenda

1. Welcome and introductions (15 min)

2. Software Heritage: everything you always wanted to know and never dared to ask (Roberto Di Cosmo, 60 min)

3. Best practices for the good SWH ambassador (Morane Gruenpeter, 15 min)

4. Discussion & activity (25 min)

5. closing (5 min)


